chapter.para:
The xliffRoundTrip tool in an open source tool (http://sourceforge.net/projects/xliffroundtrip/
) that makes use of the XLIFF (http://www.oasis-open.org/committees/tc_home.php?wg_abbrev=xliff
) open standard. It enables a user to perform a round trip between
any well-formed XML, to XLIFF, and back to the well-formed XML.
